=== 蘋果 ===
蘋果在聲明上表示對事件感到難過，並已立即與富士康高層會談，同時展開一個對富士康應對員工自殺處理方法的獨立調查<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/1151555/foxconn.html |title=Apple: 'Saddened and upset' by latest Foxconn deaths |access-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120830071749/http://www.macworld.com/article/1151555/foxconn.html |archive-date=2012-08-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，另外亦提供補貼予富士康員工<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nb.zol.com.cn/180/1804089.html |title=苹果公司称将直接补贴富士康员工 |access-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920180041/http://nb.zol.com.cn/180/1804089.html |archive-date=2013-09-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。蘋果於其後的供應商責任報告書中也提出了多項保障員工的措施<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.apple.com/supplierresponsibility/pdf/Apple_SR_2011_Progress_Report.pdf |title=Apple Supplier Responsibility 2011 Progress Report |access-date=2013-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130407210122/https://www.apple.com/supplierresponsibility/pdf/Apple_SR_2011_Progress_Report.pdf |archive-date=2013-04-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

